Student Database & Fee Receipt System
Overview
This project provides a structured Excel workbook for managing student records and fee receipts at NKS Coding Area.
It helps track student enrollment, course fees, monthly payments, and generate official receipts.

Contents
- Students Database
- Registration number
- Student & guardian details
- Course name and fees
- Monthly fee tracking (Aprilâ€“March)
- Received and remaining fees
- Fee Receipt Template
- Registration number
- Student & guardian details
- Course and fee information
- Paid amount & month of payment
- Remaining balance
- Amount in words
- Signature field

Usage
- Open Copilot.xlsx in Microsoft Excel.
- Enter student details in the Students Database sheet.
- Update monthly fee records as payments are received.
- Use the Fee Receipt sheet to generate receipts for students.

Features
- Centralized student record management
- Monthly fee tracking across the academic year
- Professional receipt format with amount in words
- Easy customization for new students and courses
